gpyfft, a python wrapper for the OpenCL FFT library APPML/clAmdFft from AMD


Requirements:
-------------

python
cython
pyopencl
APPML clAmdFft 1.8
AMD APP

Installation:
-------------

* install clAmdFft, add clAmdFft/binXX to PATH (or copy
  clAmdFft.Runtime.dll to package directory), edit setup.py to point
  to clAmdFft and AMD APP directories.

* python setup.py install

* or inplace build:
  python setup.py build_ext --inplace

License:
--------

GPL

Tested on: 
----------

Windows 7 64bit, Python 2.7, AMD APP 2.7, AMD 6850, 

